    # Z "No, you're fine. I mean you look very nice."
    Z "No, estás bien. Quiero decir que estás muy guapa."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:83
translate spanish d4c_b528a747:

    # Z "Sorry, you know I shouldn't do this."
    Z "Lo siento, sabes que no debería hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:86
translate spanish d4c_fe81ebae:

    # Z "You're becoming a real Stalker.. Fighting fit too."
    Z "Te estás convirtiendo en una verdadera Acechadora. Y también estás en plena forma."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:87
translate spanish d4c_5ab3574d_3:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:88
translate spanish d4c_10e43ed9:

    # Zt "I shouldn't be looking at her like this."
    Zt "No debería estar mirándola así."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:89
translate spanish d4c_b9995e46:

    # Z "Our mission was a success by the way. The Queen will want to see you soon."
    Z "Por cierto, nuestra misión ha sido un éxito. La Reina querrá verte pronto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:90
translate spanish d4c_77ae1499:

    # Z "So we should be prepared for that. See you later, honey."
    Z "Así que deberíamos estar preparados para ello. Hasta luego, cariño."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:93
translate spanish d4c_4c6e4f7e:

    # Zt "You fucking idiot [persistent.player_name]!"
    Zt "¡Puto imbécil, [persistent.player_name]!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:94
translate spanish d4c_f2452995:

    # Zt "Why is talking to her always so complicated?!?"
    Zt "¿Por qué hablar con ella siempre es tan complicado?!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:95
translate spanish d4c_3e927064:

    # Zt "If I really want her to become the Stalker she could be, I should not allow her to be claimed."
    Zt "Si realmente quiero que se convierta en la Acechadora que podría ser, no debo permitir que la reclamen."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:96
translate spanish d4c_7e47c02d:

    # Zt "She can not be taken by you, [persistent.player_name]."
    Zt "Ella no puede ser tomada por ti, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:97
translate spanish d4c_10ff68f4:

    # Zt "Stop thinking with your heart or dick, just for once."
    Zt "Deja de pensar con el corazón o la polla, solo por una vez."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:98
translate spanish d4c_f6c35e2d:

    # Zt "..."
    Zt "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:105
translate spanish d4c_3dc0168e:

    # Z "No, it's just..."
    Z "No, es que..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:106
translate spanish d4c_c507de07:

    # Z "I got a bit distracted."
    Z "Me distraje un poco."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:107
translate spanish d4c_14d4e1ae:

    # Z "The Queen also said that today, new caravans have reached Zeta unimpeded, once the storm settled."
    Z "La Reina también ha dicho que hoy han llegado nuevas caravanas a Zeta sin obstáculos, una vez que se ha asentado la tormenta."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:108
translate spanish d4c_20e01930:

    # Z "So it seems to have worked out."
    Z "Así que parece que ha funcionado."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:111
translate spanish d4c_dcf0272e:

    # S "That's very good to hear."
    S "Es muy bueno oírlo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:112
translate spanish d4c_fa79a6c6:

    # S "It seems our mission was a success then."
    S "Parece que nuestra misión fue un éxito entonces."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:115
translate spanish d4c_462a19f1:

    # Z "Yes.. oh, and another thing..."
    Z "Sí... oh, y otra cosa..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:116
translate spanish d4c_7b0751d3:

    # Z "The Queen wants to see you."
    Z "La Reina quiere verte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:119
translate spanish d4c_835b0445:

    # S "What?!"
    S "¡¿Qué?!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:120
translate spanish d4c_dfc7557c:

    # S "Why?!"
    S "¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:123
translate spanish d4c_97f84c19:

    # Z "I don't know. She said that she wants to see you, since you're my novice."
    Z "No lo sé. Ha dicho que quiere verte, ya que eres mi novicia."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:126
translate spanish d4c_f6489bb1:

    # S "...Now I'm nervous."
    S "... Ahora estoy nerviosa."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:129
translate spanish d4c_a24b1427:

    # Z "And I am curious. But we'll see. Her argument does make sense."
    Z "Y tengo curiosidad. Pero ya veremos. Su argumento tiene sentido."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:130
translate spanish d4c_390bafcf:

    # Z "You're being trained as a Desert Stalker, not a common foot soldier."
    Z "Te están entrenando como Acechadora del Desierto, no como una simple soldado raso."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:131
translate spanish d4c_d107685c:

    # Z "Just be yourself and remember your lessons. She's not much older than you after all."
    Z "Sólo sé tú misma y recuerda tus lecciones. Al fin y al cabo, no es mucho mayor que tú."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:132
translate spanish d4c_d16b5af8:

    # Z "I'm sure you'll be fine."
    Z "Estoy seguro de que lo harás bien."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:135
translate spanish d4c_790393d1:

    # Z "I'm heading out now, [S]."
    Z "Me voy ya, [S]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:136
translate spanish d4c_ef251155:

    # Z "Catch you later, alright?"
    Z "Hasta luego, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:139
translate spanish d4c_091695ea:

    # S "Sure [persistent.dad]. Speak soon."
    S "Claro [persistent.dad]. Hablamos pronto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:147
translate spanish d4e_e382c94d:

    # Zt "[E] should be here any second now..."
    Zt "[E] debería estar aquí en cualquier momento..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:150
translate spanish d4e_6c79f2e2:

    # "As you enter the room, you see Emilia looking around..."
    "Al entrar en la habitación, ves a Emilia mirando a su alrededor..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:152
translate spanish d4e_6befafaa:

    # Z "Hello [E]. I understand you have finished emptying the spare room upstairs?"
    Z "Hola [E]. ¿Tengo entendido que has terminado de vaciar la habitación de arriba?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:155
translate spanish d4e_a4f3bb0a:

    # E "Yes [mas], as you ordered."
    E "Sí [mas], como has ordenado."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:158
translate spanish d4e_65ceffa2:

    # Z "Very well. I know [W] has informed you about our little surprise for [A]."
    Z "Muy bien. Sé que [W] te ha informado de nuestra pequeña sorpresa para [A]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:159
translate spanish d4e_4efbcd5b:

    # Z "This means the builders will be able to do up the room with the new furniture."
    Z "Esto significa que los constructores podrán arreglar la habitación con los nuevos muebles."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:160
translate spanish d4e_ce571eca:

    # Z "And that this room becomes available, so I want you to have it."
    Z "Y que esta habitación queda disponible, así que quiero que te la quedes."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:163
translate spanish d4e_6b736fee:

    # E "Master, come again?"
    E "Amo, ¿cómo dice?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:164
translate spanish d4e_53cb83fd:

    # E "I don't understand?"
    E "No lo entiendo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:167
translate spanish d4e_ae7d2605:

    # Z "It's simple, Emilia. This is your room now."
    Z "Es sencillo, Emilia. Esta es tu habitación ahora."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:168
translate spanish d4e_10dca2e7:

    # Z "I'm serious."
    Z "Lo digo en serio."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:170
translate spanish d4e_8f4b8c94:

    # Z "There you are, [E]."
    Z "Ahí estás, [E]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:173
translate spanish d4e_f1957c45:

    # E "Hello, [mas], I have prepared the guestroom as you instructed."
    E "Hola, [mas], he preparado la habitación de invitados como me has indicado."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:176
translate spanish d4e_4c46b73b:

    # Z "About that. I wasn't being truthful with you."
    Z "Sobre eso. No estaba siendo sincero contigo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:177
translate spanish d4e_21385bde:

    # Z "You see, this room is meant for you."
    Z "Verás, esta habitación está pensada para ti."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:180
translate spanish d4e_8e0d5fd1:

    # E "[mas]..."
    E "[mas]..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:181
translate spanish d4e_5df61c4c:

    # E "If this is some kind of joke, I would understand..."
    E "Si esto es una especie de broma, lo entendería..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:184
translate spanish d4e_7f4e08c9:

    # Z "This is not a joke, [E]."
    Z "Esto no es una broma, [E]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:185
translate spanish d4e_fdc4a589:

    # Z "[W] and I have agreed that now that [A]'s room is being prepared, her old room should serve a new purpose."
    Z "[W] y yo hemos acordado que ahora que se está preparando la habitación de [A], su antigua habitación debe servir para un nuevo propósito."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:188
translate spanish d4e_689ec700:

    # Z "What better use than to give you a measure of comfort? We have the room for it and you're doing a good job."
    Z "¿Qué mejor uso que darte un poco de comodidad? Tenemos espacio para ello y estás haciendo un buen trabajo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:189
translate spanish d4e_3ba4ff58:

    # E "I..."
    E "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:192
translate spanish d4e_3c8e10a6:

    # E "Thank you, [mas]."
    E "Gracias, [mas]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:193
translate spanish d4e_b07f2945:

    # E "I have never..."
    E "Nunca he..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:194
translate spanish d4e_003cb6c0:

    # E "[Q]'s palace was beautiful, and I was treated fairly well there..."
    E "El palacio de [Q] era hermoso, y me trataron bastante bien allí..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:195
translate spanish d4e_978246ac:

    # E "But my own room... I could've never considered it possible..."
    E "Pero mi propia habitación... Nunca lo hubiera considerado posible..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:196
translate spanish d4e_ecf9c0fc:

    # E "Thank you so much."
    E "Muchas gracias."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:202
translate spanish d4e_c1c0f556:

    # Z "You deserve it."
    Z "Te lo mereces."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:203
translate spanish d4e_b49fd9a3:

    # Z "I knew you were a good servant the day you came here."
    Z "Sabía que eras una buena sirvienta el día que llegaste aquí."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:204
translate spanish d4e_ca71f794:

    # Z "[W] also trusts you."
    Z "[W] también confía en ti."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:207
translate spanish d4e_ed4f51b3:

    # Z "So you deserve your own room."
    Z "Para que te merezcas tu propia habitación."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:208
translate spanish d4e_9eaa127e:

    # Z "There is one other issue, however."
    Z "Sin embargo, hay otra cuestión."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:209
translate spanish d4e_798e06bc:

    # Z "[W] will give you your own collar soon."
    Z "[W] te pondrá tu propio collar pronto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:210
translate spanish d4e_6dd7d43a:

    # Z "We need to make sure people know that you are our servant."
    Z "Necesitamos que la gente sepa que eres nuestra sirvienta."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:213
translate spanish d4e_616c0bfb:

    # E "I will gladly wear it, [mas]."
    E "Lo llevaré con gusto, [mas]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:216
translate spanish d4e_e8dc0b42:

    # Z "Good."
    Z "Bien."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:217
translate spanish d4e_50292524:

    # Z "I will go now."
    Z "Me iré ahora."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:218
translate spanish d4e_2e868d7a:

    # Z "It's almost time for dinner, don't make my wife wait too long."
    Z "Ya casi es la hora de cenar, no hagas esperar demasiado a mi mujer."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:221
translate spanish d4e_5453efe1:

    # E "Yes, [mas]."
    E "Sí, [mas]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:222
translate spanish d4e_865e121a:

    # E "Thank you."
    E "Gracias."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:223
translate spanish d4e_2c39c429:

    # E "I will do my best to earn my place."
    E "Haré todo lo posible para ganarme el puesto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:227
translate spanish d4e_5eeacb49:

    # Z "[W] and I decided that you can keep [A]'s old room."
    Z "[W] y yo hemos decidido que puedes quedarte con la antigua habitación de [A]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:228
translate spanish d4e_8152cc6b:

    # Z "A good maid deserves her own space."
    Z "Una buena criada se merece su propio espacio."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:229
translate spanish d4e_b9cb2508:

    # Z "It is also important for the image of a household that all its members are well cared for."
    Z "También es importante para la imagen de un hogar que todos sus miembros estén bien cuidados."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:230
translate spanish d4e_bad26895:

    # Z "However, we expect you to do your work in return."
    Z "Sin embargo, esperamos que hagas tu trabajo a cambio."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:231
translate spanish d4e_d283e8d7:

    # Z "You will also have to wear a collar from now on. [W] will have it made for you."
    Z "También tendrás que llevar un collar a partir de ahora. [W] lo mandará hacer para ti."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:232
translate spanish d4e_a087415c:

    # Z "Finally, if I tell you to serve me or my guests when they come to visit, you will do so."
    Z "Por último, si te digo que me sirvas a mí o a mis invitados cuando vengan de visita, lo harás."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:235
translate spanish d4e_e7e3987e:

    # E "I will, [mas]. Without hesitation."
    E "Lo haré, [mas]. Sin dudarlo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:238
translate spanish d4e_52929da3:

    # Z "I believe you. [W] only told me good things about you."
    Z "Te creo. [W] sólo me ha dicho cosas buenas de ti."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:239
translate spanish d4e_50292524_1:

    # Z "I will go now."
    Z "Me iré ahora."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:240
translate spanish d4e_a5986279:

    # Z "It's almost time for dinner, so you better not make my wife wait too long."
    Z "Ya casi es la hora de la cena, así que será mejor que no hagas esperar a mi mujer demasiado tiempo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:241
translate spanish d4e_5453efe1_1:

    # E "Yes, [mas]."
    E "Sí, [mas]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:244
translate spanish d4e_24a348fe:

    # "She bows before you..."
    "Ella se inclina ante ti..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:247
translate spanish d4e_3a991f1a:

    # E "I am thankful for the opportunity you give me."
    E "Te agradezco la oportunidad que me brindas."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:248
translate spanish d4e_d37541ec:

    # E "If you need anything, I am here to serve."
    E "Si necesitas algo, estoy aquí para servirte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:252
translate spanish d4e_ee902196:

    # Z "That was my wife's idea."
    Z "Eso fue idea de mi mujer."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:253
translate spanish d4e_950c45e5:

    # Z "She knows that it is important for the image of a household to have well cared for servants."
    Z "Ella sabe que es importante para la imagen de un hogar tener a los sirvientes bien atendidos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:254
translate spanish d4e_4fb4344d:

    # Z "But I advise you to not get complacent about your new room."
    Z "Pero te aconsejo que no te confíes por tu nueva habitación."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:257
translate spanish d4e_16dea8bb:

    # Z "You are still our servant and will do whatever I, your mistress or my [persistent.da]s say."
    Z "Sigues siendo nuestra sierva y harás lo que yo, tu ama o mis [persistent.da]s te digan."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:258
translate spanish d4e_0fbd22cd:

