    Q "... sólo será una charla amistosa entre nosotras."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1195
translate spanish d4g_70237aff:

    # Q "If she is to become an elite member in my ranks, I should get to know and evaluate her."
    Q "Si va a convertirse en un miembro de la élite en mis filas, debo conocerla y evaluarla."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1198
translate spanish d4g_08ac1264:

    # Q "Now... Let me think about your reward..."
    Q "Ahora... Déjame pensar en tu recompensa..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1201
translate spanish d4g_9d680564:

    # Q "Hmm..."
    Q "Hmm..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1202
translate spanish d4g_44d28e26:

    # "She takes her time before answering, to the point that you wonder whether she is actually thinking about it or is rather leaving you hanging for her own enjoyment..."
    "Se toma su tiempo antes de responder, hasta el punto de que te preguntas si realmente lo está pensando o más bien te está dejando colgado para su propio disfrute..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1205
translate spanish d4g_366dbc66:

    # Q "I will grant you the privilege of access to my personal thermae for a day."
    Q "Te concederé el privilegio de acceder a mis termas personales durante un día."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1206
translate spanish d4g_e171d17d:

    # Q "You will be attended to by my slaves during your stay."
    Q "Serás atendido por mis esclavas durante tu estancia."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1209
translate spanish d4g_2ceee314:

    # Q "...and you know what they say about royal slaves, Stalker..."
    Q "...y ya sabes lo que dicen de los esclavas reales, Acechador..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1210
translate spanish d4g_ab61dd6c:

    # Q "Their \"assistance\" goes a long way."
    Q "Su \"asistencia\" llega muy lejos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1213
translate spanish d4g_51f7dd1e:

    # Q "Now, if you mean to accept my offer, there is only one little thing I do need you to do..."
    Q "Ahora bien, si pretendes aceptar mi oferta, sólo hay una pequeña cosa que necesito que hagas..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1216
translate spanish d4g_9b40f6ac:

    # Q "...You know what that is."
    Q "... ya sabes lo que es."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1220
translate spanish d4g_90b38c0b:

    # Q "A second chance..."
    Q "Una segunda oportunidad..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1221
translate spanish d4g_3979e584:

    # Zt "Again, she treats me like a common servant..."
    Zt "De nuevo, me trata como a un vulgar sirviente..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1223
translate spanish d4g_245eac00:

    # Q "Much like last time.."
    Q "Como la última vez.."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1224
translate spanish d4g_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1230
translate spanish d4g_5351d493:

    # Z "I know what I need to do, yes."
    Z "Sé lo que tengo que hacer, sí."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1233
translate spanish d4g_8d147499:

    # Q "What are you..."
    Q "¿Qué estás..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1236
translate spanish d4g_190a906f:

    # Q "Whaa?!!"
    Q "¡¡¿Queee?!!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1237
translate spanish d4g_2b58a526:

    # "{i}You pull her a little towards you..."
    "{i}La atraes un poco hacia ti..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1240
translate spanish d4g_4a60778c:

    # Z "I accept your reward..."
    Z "Acepto tu recompensa..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1241
translate spanish d4g_011fe0c6:

    # Z "But I think we both know that I am much more than a servant to you."
    Z "Pero creo que ambos sabemos que soy mucho más que un sirviente para ti."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1242
translate spanish d4g_812107ea:

    # Z "You very well know my name, and I deserve to be treated with a little more respect, don't you think?"
    Z "Sabes muy bien cómo me llamo, y merezco que me trates con un poco más de respeto, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1245
translate spanish d4g_5d74a46f:

    # Z "After all, I risk my life for you every time you call on my services."
    Z "Después de todo, arriesgo mi vida por ti cada vez que solicitas mis servicios."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1246
translate spanish d4g_ef67d1e3:

    # Q "I...uh..."
    Q "Yo... eh..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1249
translate spanish d4g_c867ff35:

    # Q "...never denied that..."
    Q "... nunca he negado que..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1252
translate spanish d4g_0d8e833d:

    # "{i}You kiss her hand slowly..."
    "{i}Besas su mano lentamente..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1253
translate spanish d4g_6ae95c82:

    # Q "You are... one of my most experienced men, after all."
    Q "Eres... uno de mis hombres más experimentados, después de todo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1256
translate spanish d4g_6f8092b6:

    # Q "Very well..."
    Q "Muy bien..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1259
translate spanish d4g_6b28300e:

    # Q "As long as you stay loyal to me, you will be treated fairly."
    Q "Mientras te mantengas leal a mí, se te tratará con justicia."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1260
translate spanish d4g_f38a92a4:

    # Qw "Now, unhand me, before my guards punish your indiscretion..."
    Qw "Ahora, suéltame, antes de que mis guardias castiguen tu indiscreción..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1263
translate spanish d4g_eccb0c7f:

    # Z "As you wish."
    Z "Como desees."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1266
translate spanish d4g_36652cbc:

    # Q "Thank you for your visit..."
    Q "Gracias por tu visita..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1267
translate spanish d4g_52bee2b9:

    # Q "...Stalker [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "... Acechador [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1268
translate spanish d4g_fc691734:

    # Q "I will let you know when I have a new mission for you."
    Q "Te avisaré cuando tenga una nueva misión para ti."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1271
translate spanish d4g_4836e2d8:

    # Z "Until next time, then."
    Z "Hasta la próxima, pues."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1276
translate spanish d4g_58b4bf82:

    # "{i}You leave the temple..."
    "{i}Sales del templo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1283
translate spanish d4g_04a9a6c1:

    # Z "That's enough."
    Z "Eso es suficiente."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1286
translate spanish d4g_125a93d2:

    # Q "...?"
    Q "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1289
translate spanish d4g_57ed44dc:

    # "You stand up..."
    "Levántate..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1290
translate spanish d4g_161c2755:

    # Q "What on earth-"
    Q "¿Qué demonios...?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1293
translate spanish d4g_6bda8a73:

    # Q "Agh-!"
    Q "¡Agh-!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1294
translate spanish d4g_79f78815:

    # G "What is he...?!"
    G "¿Qué está...?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1297
translate spanish d4g_9dd3e3a2:

    # G "Hey! Stop it right now, Stalker!"
    G "¡Eh! ¡Para ahora mismo, Acechador!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1300
translate spanish d4g_ecce4986:

    # "Your tone is unmistakably aggressive and laced with mockery..."
    "Tu tono es claramente agresivo y cargado de burla..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1301
translate spanish d4g_8712f4b8:

    # Z "With all due respect, my Queen..."
    Z "Con el debido respeto, mi Reina..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1302
translate spanish d4g_0a4022fc:

    # Z "I will no longer tolerate you belittling me or my service."
    Z "No toleraré más que me menosprecies a mí o a mi servicio."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1303
translate spanish d4g_0f2eb5a9:

    # Q "Ngh-"
    Q "Ngh..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1304
translate spanish d4g_ea2cb034:

    # Z "You are well aware of my name. I have been serving as a Desert Stalker for decades, since before you ascended to the throne."
    Z "Conoces bien mi nombre. Llevo décadas sirviendo como Acechador del Desierto, desde antes de que tú ascendieras al trono."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1305
translate spanish d4g_5a65aaad:

    # Z "I am loyal to my home, to Zeta, and to the throne."
    Z "Soy leal a mi hogar, a Zeta y al trono."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1306
translate spanish d4g_576bfb2f:

    # Z "But I will not stand to be disrespected by a girl half my age, even if she happens to be the Queen."
    Z "Pero no soportaré que me falte al respeto una chica de la mitad de mi edad, aunque resulte ser la Reina."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1309
translate spanish d4g_7aa837aa:

    # Q "Hngh... G-guards...-"
    Q "Hngh... G-guardias...-"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1310
translate spanish d4g_a0b7c65f:

    # Z "Have I made myself clear?!"
    Z "¿Me he explicado bien?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1313
translate spanish d4g_ce4157ec:

    # "{i}She subtly starts to nod..."
    "{i}Ella empieza a asentir sutilmente..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1314
translate spanish d4g_d5080931:

    # G "Have you lost your mind?!"
    G "¿Has perdido la cabeza?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1315
translate spanish d4g_8d1104b9:

    # G "Grab him!"
    G "¡Agarradlo!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1318
translate spanish d4g_b2b015d8:

    # "{i}A guard forcefully grabs you and drags you away..."
    "{i}Un guardia te agarra a la fuerza y te arrastra..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1321
translate spanish d4g_1257ff92:

    # Q "I-I didn't expect this."
    Q "No me esperaba esto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1322
translate spanish d4g_160cdf71:

    # Q "Get him out of here..."
    Q "Sacadlo de aquí..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1327
translate spanish d4g_4730e4dc:

    # "{i}You are forced to leave the temple..."
    "{i}Te ves obligado a abandonar el templo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1334
translate spanish d4h_3e8bc1f1:

    # Zt "Well.. That had to be said."
    Zt "Bueno... Eso tenía que decirse."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1335
translate spanish d4h_49eaeaa0:

    # Zt "She may be a Queen, but her childish antics have to stop."
    Zt "Puede ser una Reina, pero sus payasadas infantiles deben parar."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1337
translate spanish d4h_e0b6c73f:

    # Zt "Play the long game, [persistent.player_name]."
    Zt "Juega a largo plazo, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1341
translate spanish d4h_f1c41870:

    # Zt "She should be glad I'm working for her at all..."
    Zt "Debería estar agradecida de que esté trabajando para ella en absoluto..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1342
translate spanish d4h_1f17e2dd:

    # Zt "...not every Stalker does. Certainly not as gladly or efficiently as I do."
    Zt "... no todos los Acechador lo hacen. Ciertamente no tan alegre o eficientemente como yo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1344
translate spanish d4h_52e2e7c2:

    # Zt "She likes to play tough... I guess being the Queen is a lonely job."
    Zt "Le gusta hacerse la dura... Supongo que ser Reina es un trabajo solitario."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1348
translate spanish d4h_32903a60:

    # Z "Time to go home..."
    Z "Es hora de ir a casa..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1353
translate spanish d4h_56fda395:

    # "{i}Meanwhile...{w=1.}{nw}"
    "{i}Mientras tanto...{w=1.}{nw}"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1391
translate spanish d4b_60261d66:

    # Z "...just my luck."
    Z "... sólo mi suerte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1394
translate spanish d4b_2057725c:

    # Zt "This damn storm showing up out of nowhere, right when I'm on a mission on direct orders from the Queen herself."
    Zt "Esta maldita tormenta apareció de la nada, justo cuando estoy en una misión con órdenes directas de la Reina."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1395
translate spanish d4b_1e38f091:

    # Zt "Almost ruined it..."
    Zt "Casi lo arruinas..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1396
translate spanish d4b_783818bf:

    # Zt "And now the car is paying the price."
    Zt "Y ahora el coche está pagando el precio."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1399
translate spanish d4b_9ec0d336:

    # Zt "[S] must've gotten scared shitless too."
    Zt "[S] también debió haberse asustado muchísimo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1400
translate spanish d4b_f2488d94:

    # Zt "Damn it..."
    Zt "Joder…"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1401
translate spanish d4b_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1404
translate spanish d4b_bc4a1436:

    # Z "Hey [W]... {i}*sighs*"
    Z "Oye, [W]... {i}*suspiros*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1405
translate spanish d4b_df037978:

    # W "Hey love... Are you mad at the engine, the sand, or is this still about the mission?"
    W "Oye, amor... ¿Estás enfadado con el motor, con la arena, o todavía se trata de la misión?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1406
translate spanish d4b_d8084139:

    # Z "The day started out so well.."
    Z "El día empezó tan bien.."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1409
translate spanish d4b_ca72d923:

    # W "I understand that..."
    W "Lo entiendo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1410
translate spanish d4b_7b752d9c:

    # W "But you must put it in the past now. The wind and the sand will not be tied to the wants of men."
    W "Pero ahora debes dejarlo en el pasado. El viento y la arena no estarán atados a los deseos de los hombres."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1411
translate spanish d4b_5a54ebf3:

    # W "You told me the Queen understood and accepted your explanation."
    W "Me dijiste que la Reina había entendido y aceptado tu explicación."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1412
translate spanish d4b_c1c2c019:

    # Z "Well, she had some strong words to say, yesterday."
    Z "Pues bien, ayer tuvo unas palabras contundentes."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1413
translate spanish d4b_84240750:

    # W "What matters most, you and [S] are alive."
    W "Lo más importante es que tú y [S] estáis vivos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1414
translate spanish d4b_a4531d8f:

    # Z "Yes... you're right.{i} *sighs*"
    Z "Sí... tienes razón.{i} *suspiros*"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1415
translate spanish d4b_5f2991c6:

    # Z "Thank you, [W]."
    Z "Gracias, [W]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1416
translate spanish d4b_4f693e33:

    # W "So... how about my handsome husband takes the rest of the day off and escorts his women to the market?"
    W "Y... ¿qué tal si mi guapo marido se toma el resto del día libre y acompaña a sus mujeres al mercado?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1417
translate spanish d4b_65e7178c:

    # W "You know the girls would like it."
    W "Sabes que a las chicas les gustaría."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1418
translate spanish d4b_4fd7a4ea:

    # W "And I too would like to spend the day with my man."
    W "Y a mí también me gustaría pasar el día con mi hombre."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1419
translate spanish d4b_6c5b7343:

    # Z "I guess..."
    Z "Supongo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1420
translate spanish d4b_d977a252:

    # Z "I could use a break, yes."
    Z "Me vendría bien un descanso, sí."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1421
translate spanish d4b_cd030247:

    # Z "And I guess the builders will be a disturbance anyway."
    Z "Y supongo que los constructores serán una molestia de todos modos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1422
translate spanish d4b_872ec620:

    # W "Yes, I can see them coming."
    W "Sí, puedo verlos venir."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1426
translate spanish d4b_8dccb176:

    # Z "I will let the girls know that we will head out soon."
    Z "Informaré a las chicas de que saldremos pronto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1427
translate spanish d4b_a07786a8:

    # W "Thank you. I will go get changed."
    W "Gracias. Iré a cambiarme."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1428
translate spanish d4b_cdc7647b:

    # W "See you in a bit."
    W "Nos vemos dentro de un rato."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1431
translate spanish d4b_1973e2a7:

    # "{i}Soon after..."
    "{i}Poco después..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1434
translate spanish d4b_5b348411:

    # A "I'm serious, [S]..."
    A "Lo digo en serio, [S]..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1435
translate spanish d4b_739859af:

    # S "Yeah yeah, of course..."
    S "Sí, sí, por supuesto..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1436
translate spanish d4b_c450cf28:

    # A "No, for real!! I am getting fatter."
    A "¡¡No, de verdad!! Estoy engordando."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1437
translate spanish d4b_9739e8ad:

    # S "You are being ridiculous."
    S "Estás haciendo el ridículo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1438
translate spanish d4b_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1440
translate spanish d4b_ed64be93:

    # A "Maybe it's because I'm too short."
    A "Tal vez sea porque soy muy bajita."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1441
translate spanish d4b_52160a07:

    # S "That might be it."
    S "Puede que sea eso."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1442
translate spanish d4b_894312e2:

    # A "Meanie..."
    A "Malvada..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1443
translate spanish d4b_cb964fdc:

    # A "[S]?"
    A "¡[S]!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1444
translate spanish d4b_20c04949:

    # S "Yes?"
    S "¿Sí?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1446
translate spanish d4b_fe41a87b:

    # A "What do you think of [E]?"
    A "¿Qué piensas de [E]?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1447
translate spanish d4b_05ffeee6:

    # S "She's nice... a little too nice for my taste."
    S "Es simpática... demasiado simpática para mi gusto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1448
translate spanish d4b_9baa0765:

    # A "I know right..."
    A "Lo sé bien..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1449
translate spanish d4b_e2cf69f0:

    # A "She agrees to everything..."
    A "Ella está de acuerdo con todo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1450
translate spanish d4b_a08c718b:

    # A "And I mean e v e r y t h i n g."
    A "Y me refiero a  T O D O."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1451
translate spanish d4b_56de7cca:

    # A "She even kneels on command!"
    A "Incluso se arrodilla cuando se le ordena."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1452
translate spanish d4b_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1453
translate spanish d4b_e3749ed0:

    # S "Well, yes...I mean, she has to."
    S "Bueno, sí... quiero decir, tiene que hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1454
translate spanish d4b_11ea656f:

    # A "Yes..."
    A "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1455
translate spanish d4b_8755fb04:

    # A "Yes she has to."
    A "Sí, tiene que hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1456
translate spanish d4b_37758234:

    # A "{i}*sigh...*"
    A "{i}*suspiro...*"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1459
translate spanish d4b_cf5f31da:

    # A "Say... do you think guys like short girls like me?"
    A "Dime... ¿crees que a los chicos les gustan las chicas bajitas como yo?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1461
translate spanish d4b_4cd99b18:

    # S "That's a sudden change of topic..."
    S "Eso es un cambio de tema repentino..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1462
translate spanish d4b_9bc0a6d6:

    # S "If you must know..."
    S "Si quieres saberlo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1465
translate spanish d4b_497341dd:

    # S "I think you're a little too obsessed with attention, [A]."
    S "Creo que estás demasiado obsesionada con la atención, [A]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1466
translate spanish d4b_f44c357d:

    # A "I'm not..."
    A "No lo estoy..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1469
translate spanish d4b_551d5d82:

    # A "I just like how people look at me."
    A "Sólo me gusta cómo me mira la gente."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1470
translate spanish d4b_20a67c26:

    # S "{i}*sigh...*"
    S "{i}*suspiro...*"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1473
translate spanish d4b_72591406:

    # S "Hey [persistent.dad]..."
    S "Oye, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1474
translate spanish d4b_52881756:

    # Z "Hey you two."
    Z "Hola a las dos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1477
translate spanish d4b_3123359e:

    # A "Hi [persistent.dad]!!"
    A "¡¡Hola [persistent.dad]!!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1478
translate spanish d4b_97cac9ad:

    # S "Wahh! [A]!"
    S "¡Ahh! ¡[A]!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1480
translate spanish d4b_d3222d0b:

    # A "Did [persistent.mom] ask you about taking us to the market?"
    A "¿Te ha pedido [persistent.mom] que nos lleves al mercado?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1482
translate spanish d4b_3d797dd7:

    # Z "Yes, I came here to tell you just that."
    Z "Sí, he venido para deciros precisamente eso."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1483
translate spanish d4b_b45b6424:

    # Z "You girls should get ready."
    Z "Deberíais prepararos, chicas."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1484
translate spanish d4b_111d1dfc:

    # A "You deserve a hug for that..."
    A "Te mereces un abrazo por ello..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1486
translate spanish d4b_2768839d:

    # S "There she goes again..."
    S "Ahí está ella de nuevo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1487
translate spanish d4b_adb4e8e7:

    # S "Seeking your attention like a child."
    S "Buscando tu atención como una niña."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1488
translate spanish d4b_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1490
translate spanish d4b_d50ffdbc:

    # S "I don't think she'd last a week without your hands on her..."
    S "No creo que durara una semana sin que le pusieras las manos encima..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1492
translate spanish d4b_a6c0cc2c:

    # A "What of it, huh?"
    A "¿Y qué, eh?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1493
translate spanish d4b_3d34d0e1:

    # A "I like being with [persistent.dad], what's your problem?"
    A "Me gusta estar con [persistent.dad], ¿cuál es tu problema?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1499
translate spanish d4b_8a7f14aa:

    # A "Hn..."
    A "Hn..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1500
translate spanish d4b_f8122ff8:

    # A "...and I think he likes to see me too."
    A "... y creo que a él también le gusta verme."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1502
translate spanish d4b_6321d310:

    # S "I wasn't talking about that..."
    S "No estaba hablando de eso..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1503
translate spanish d4b_5da92feb:

    # S "And stop suggesting he likes you more..."
    S "Y deja de sugerir que tú le gustas más..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1505
translate spanish d4b_4d8298c0:

    # A "I wasn't suggesting anything, sis..."
    A "No estaba sugiriendo nada, hermana..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1506
translate spanish d4b_5410f889:

    # A "But I think I'm not the one who has an issue here."
    A "Pero creo que aquí no soy yo la que tiene un problema."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1510
translate spanish d4b_a216a6b2:

    # S "That's not what I was talking about..."
    S "No es de eso de lo que hablaba..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1511
translate spanish d4b_fd92abe0:

    # S "I like to be with him too."
    S "A mí también me gusta estar con él."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1512
translate spanish d4b_f45fff30:

    # S "But do you see me jumping around making a fuss everytime I see him?!"
    S "¡¿Pero me ves saltando por ahí y montando un número cada vez que lo veo?!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1513
translate spanish d4b_7a7f9be5:

    # A "Can't I just be happy?!"
    A "¡¿No puedo simplemente ser feliz?!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1514
translate spanish d4b_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1515
translate spanish d4b_8c17a754:

    # A "I think it's not me who has a problem with attention."
    A "Creo que no soy yo quien tiene un problema de atención."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1517
translate spanish d4b_7aaa26d5:

    # A "Maybe you're the one who needs more attention from boys..."
    A "Tal vez seas tú la que necesita más atención de los chicos..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1519
translate spanish d4b_127b4933:

    # S "Argh! You're insufferable!"
    S "¡Argh! ¡Eres insufrible!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1520
translate spanish d4b_293b5b65:

    # S "One day you will regret acting like this."
    S "Un día te arrepentirás de haber actuado así."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1529
translate spanish d4b_abdd40cd:

    # S "I'm going to my room."
    S "Me voy a mi habitación."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1530
translate spanish d4b_38c07eb2:

    # S "I'll get ready, [persistent.dad]. Call me when it's time, okay?"
    S "Me prepararé, [persistent.dad]. Llámame cuando sea el momento, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1531
translate spanish d4b_d87da71b:

    # Z "I will, don't stress yourself."
    Z "Lo haré, no te estreses."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1532
translate spanish d4b_1df27437:

    # A "See you soon, sister..."
    A "Hasta pronto, hermana..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1533
translate spanish d4b_971a98df_2:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1539
translate spanish d4b_746f26d2:

    # Z "You should get ready as well, [A]."
    Z "Tú también deberías prepararte, [A]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1540
translate spanish d4b_1c60832d:

    # A "Of course, [persistent.dad]."
    A "Por supuesto, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1544
translate spanish d4b_f77609c1:

    # Z "[S]..."
    Z "[S]..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1546
translate spanish d4b_ab5b477e:

    # S "I can't stand her sometimes."
    S "A veces no la soporto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1549
translate spanish d4b_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1550
translate spanish d4b_4bdaae81:

    # "{i}You look at her with a warm smile"
    "{i}La miras con una cálida sonrisa"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1555
translate spanish d4b_971a98df_3:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1558
translate spanish d4b_62f10eb0:

    # A "Hey, uh.. [persistent.dad]?"
    A "Oye, eh... ¿[persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1560
translate spanish d4b_4455acc3:

    # Z "[S], go get changed, okay? We will leave in a while."
    Z "[S], ve a cambiarte, ¿de acuerdo? Nos iremos en un rato."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1566
translate spanish d4b_0a0a1c63:

    # S "Yes... I will get ready. "
    S "Sí... Me prepararé."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1567
translate spanish d4b_397f7553:

    # S "Give me a shout when it's time, please, [persistent.dad]."
    S "Dame un grito cuando sea la hora, por favor, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1568
translate spanish d4b_1df27437_1:

    # A "See you soon, sister..."
    A "Hasta pronto, hermana..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1569
translate spanish d4b_971a98df_4:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1575
translate spanish d4b_0c01544b:

    # Z "You should get ready as well, [A], but before you do, go see if you can help your mother getting ready."
    Z "Deberías prepararte también, [A], pero antes de hacerlo, ve a ver si puedes ayudar a tu madre a prepararse."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1576
translate spanish d4b_1c60832d_1:

    # A "Of course, [persistent.dad]."
    A "Por supuesto, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1585
translate spanish d4b26_5ad82e7a:

    # Z "Here we are ladies."
    Z "Aquí estamos señoras."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1586
translate spanish d4b26_161b2b2d:

    # Z "Don't spend all the gold I've given you at once."
    Z "No os gastéis todo el oro que os he dado de una vez."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1587
translate spanish d4b26_7fc5b8c8:

    # Z "...And stay away from shady people, okay?"
    Z "... Y alejaos de la gente sospechosa, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1588
translate spanish d4b26_6355a5d5:

    # A "Yeah yeah..."
    A "Ya ya..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1589
translate spanish d4b26_bbc8a0cb:

    # S "Got it."
    S "La tengo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1592
translate spanish d4b26_bb0848bf:

    # W "Let's go, husband."
    W "Vamos, marido."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1595
translate spanish d4b26_1e79bc92:

    # tra "Quality baskets!"
    tra "¡Cestas de calidad!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1596
translate spanish d4b26_3257746d:

    # tra "The finest in all of Zeta!"
    tra "¡Las mejores de todo Zeta!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1597
translate spanish d4b26_f1b85aec:

    # tra "[Q] herself buys her baskets from us!"
    tra "¡La misma [Q] nos compra sus cestas!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1600
translate spanish d4b26_fbbf9dc5:

    # S "I just love it here."
    S "Simplemente me encanta estar aquí."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1603
translate spanish d4b26_56ee1992:

    # S "All the different things..."
    S "Todas las cosas diferentes..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1606
translate spanish d4b26_4a81ec5d:

    # S "People come from all around Zeta and beyond, to sell their goods."
    S "La gente viene de todo Zeta y de más allá, para vender sus productos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1607
translate spanish d4b26_4d863972:

    # S "So many different cultures!"
    S "¡Tantas culturas diferentes!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1610
translate spanish d4b26_2f092f60:

    # A "Did they move the jeweler's stall?"
    A "¿Han trasladado el puesto del joyero?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1613
translate spanish d4b26_37365d75:

    # A "I want to check if they have anything nice."
    A "Quiero comprobar si tienen algo bonito."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1616
translate spanish d4b26_018f09f4:

    # A "Let me guess, you want to check out the blacksmith again?"
    A "Déjame adivinar, ¿quieres volver a ver a la herrera?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1617
translate spanish d4b26_00abd311:

    # S "Yes... I will be with you in a minute, okay?"
    S "Sí... Estaré contigo en un minuto, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1618
translate spanish d4b26_514dfb19:

    # A "Alright sis.."
    A "Muy bien, hermana..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1619
translate spanish d4b26_97d98da0:

    # A "Don't buy all the swords..."
    A "No compres todas las espadas..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1620
translate spanish d4b26_d8330810:

    # A "You already have so many."
    A "Ya tienes muchas."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1621
translate spanish d4b26_e92655d1:

    # A "It's not like you can use more than two at a time anyway, and you don't want to scare away all the boys."
    A "De todos modos, no es que puedas usar más de dos a la vez, y no querrás asustar a todos los chicos."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1622
translate spanish d4b26_08dbc1e8:

    # S "Oh stop it!"
    S "¡Oh, para!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1626
translate spanish d4b26_0f78b9f5:

    # W "Hello [Ig], nice to see you."
    W "Hola [Ig], me alegro de verte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1627
translate spanish d4b26_1e2c2b5e:

    # "{i}The man standing behind the counter starts speaking in a thick slavic accent..."
    "{i}El hombre que está detrás del mostrador comienza a hablar con un marcado acento eslavo..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1628
translate spanish d4b26_8c2fdec2:

    # Ig "Good day Lady [W]. Always pleasure to meet you."
    Ig "Buenos días Señora [W]. Siempre es un placer verte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1629
translate spanish d4b26_883c8134:

    # Ig "You look very pretty, as always."
    Ig "Estás muy guapa, como siempre."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1630
translate spanish d4b26_5bc3bcf3:

    # W "Thank you."
    W "Gracias."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1633
translate spanish d4b26_236a117d:

    # Ig "Hello old friend."
    Ig "Hola viejo amigo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1634
translate spanish d4b26_5ab00c44:

    # Z "[Ig], how are you doing?"
    Z "[Ig], ¿cómo estás?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1635
translate spanish d4b26_c35b6dfa:

    # Ig "Ah you know, nothing new. How you say, same as old?"
    Ig "Ah ya sabes, nada nuevo. ¿Cómo se dice, lo mismo de siempre?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1636
translate spanish d4b26_73a47822:

    # Zt "[Ig] has been a good friend for many years."
    Zt "[Ig] ha sido un buen amigo por muchos años."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1637
translate spanish d4b26_3514ccb7:

    # Zt "For a lowly merchant, he is well connected here in Zeta and far beyond its borders."
    Zt "Para ser un simple mercader, tiene buenos contactos aquí en Zeta y mucho más allá de sus fronteras."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1638
translate spanish d4b26_c399a6a0:

    # Zt "A good man with an honest heart."
    Zt "Un buen hombre con un corazón honesto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1639
translate spanish d4b26_17706b31:

    # Ig "As you can see, we have fresh supply of fruit."
    Ig "Como podéis ver, tenemos un suministro fresco de fruta."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1642
translate spanish d4b26_f6d770cb:

    # W "Your produce looks delicious."
    W "Tus productos tienen un aspecto delicioso."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1643
translate spanish d4b26_1b55bbb6:

    # W "I always wanted to ask, where do you grow all this?"
    W "Siempre quise preguntar, ¿dónde cultivas todo esto?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1644
translate spanish d4b26_a108b881:

    # Ig "I have good connections to different regions."
    Ig "Tengo buenas conexiones con diferentes regiones."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1645
translate spanish d4b26_dc9861cb:

    # Ig "My family farm overseas, too."
    Ig "Mi familia tiene una granja en el extranjero, también."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1646
translate spanish d4b26_44ead668:

    # Ig "But trade with Old Bari is more difficult lately, so, food more expensive."
    Ig "Pero el comercio con el Viejo Bari es más difícil últimamente, así que la comida es más cara."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1647
translate spanish d4b26_63fe45d2:

    # W "Why is that?"
    W "¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1648
translate spanish d4b26_372648a5:

    # Ig "I don't know for sure, Lady [W]."
    Ig "No lo sé con seguridad, Señora [W]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1649
translate spanish d4b26_80651069:

    # Ig "Is not problems of storm, like here, but different things."
    Ig "No es un problema de tormenta, como aquí, sino cosas diferentes."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1652
translate spanish d4b26_28194eb8:

    # Zt "This fruit look delicious ind-"
    Zt "Esta fruta parece deliciosa..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1655
translate spanish d4b26_0fc1c05d:

    # Zt "...indeed."
    Zt "... de hecho."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1656
translate spanish d4b26_6505a207:

    # Z "Hey, [Ig], I didn't know you have a daughter."
    Z "Oye, [Ig], no sabía que tenías una hija."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1657
translate spanish d4b26_4b0adcf6:

    # Ig "Haha, no no. She is not daughter."
    Ig "Jajaja, no no. No es hija."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1658
translate spanish d4b26_03f3a989:

    # Ig "This is [Ka], my niece."
    Ig "Esta es [Ka], mi sobrina."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1659
translate spanish d4b26_b9012727:

    # Ig "I always promised her to take to Egypt when she is adult."
    Ig "Siempre le había prometido que la llevaría a Egipto cuando fuera adulta."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1660
translate spanish d4b26_0a8ca352:

    # Ig "Had to break her little heart for years."
    Ig "Tuvo que romper su corazoncito durante años."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1661
translate spanish d4b26_ed36b48b:

    # Z "That's a dangerous journey for her to accompany you on."
    Z "Es un viaje peligroso para que te acompañe."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1662
translate spanish d4b26_34517a46:

    # Ig "Yes, but can [Ig] break promise to favourite niece? No."
    Ig "Sí, pero ¿puede [Ig] romper la promesa a su sobrina favorita? No."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1663
translate spanish d4b26_5bdc9907:

    # Ig "She is very shy, but curious like little mouse, haha."
    Ig "Ella es muy tímida, pero curiosa como un ratoncito, jajaja."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1664
translate spanish d4b26_52dd8871:

    # Ig "You see, when she was small kid, uncle [Ig] told her stories about mighty Desert Stalkers in Egypt."
    Ig "Verás, cuando era pequeña, el tío [Ig] le contaba historias sobre poderosos Acechadores del Desierto en Egipto."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1665
translate spanish d4b26_c62a092c:

    # Ig "Now, she finally meet one. See, [Ka]? This is Desert Stalker [persistent.player_name], friend of uncle [Ig]!"
    Ig "Ahora, por fin conoce a uno. ¿Ves, [Ka]? ¡Este es el Acechador del Desierto [persistent.player_name], amigo del tío [Ig]!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1667
translate spanish d4b26_d3a12867:

    # Z "I see!"
    Z "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1668
translate spanish d4b26_225a411d:

    # Z "Nice to meet you, [Ka]."
    Z "Encantado de conocerte, [Ka]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1671
translate spanish d4b26_83b7a7eb:

    # Ka "..."
    Ka "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1674
translate spanish d4b26_b6f857d7:

    # "{i}Meanwhile..."
    "{i}Mientras tanto..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1677
translate spanish d4b26_30f74c68:

    # S "Hello Lady [Ma]. Long time no see."
    S "Hola Señora [Ma]. Cuánto tiempo sin verte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1680
translate spanish d4b26_5f365f8f:

    # Ma "..."
    Ma "..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1683
translate spanish d4b26_f5006295:

    # Ma "A long time indeed, [S]."
    Ma "Mucho tiempo, en efecto, [S]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1684
translate spanish d4b26_b490388c:

    # Ma "You really are growing into a fine young Lady."
    Ma "Realmente te estás convirtiendo en una buena jovencita."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1685
translate spanish d4b26_ba493bcf:

    # Ma "You have filled out nicely, since I last saw you."
    Ma "Te has desarrollado muy bien, desde la última vez que te vi."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1686
translate spanish d4b26_596e0fa2:

    # S "Thank you very much, [Ma]. You are looking as elegant as ever."
    S "Muchas gracias, [Ma]. Estás tan elegante como siempre."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1689
translate spanish d4b26_520b07ae:

    # Ma "So... how is my former student doing?"
    Ma "Y... ¿cómo le va a mi antigua alumna?"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1697
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_63ef43aa:

    # S "I am doing very well, thank you for asking."
    S "Estoy muy bien, gracias por preguntar."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1698
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_f7d1935f:

    # Ma "I am glad to hear that, [S]."
    Ma "Me alegro de oírlo, [S]."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1703
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_5f769f39:

    # S "I have not had to use your advanced lessons yet, so far. I have been lucky."
    S "Hasta ahora no he tenido que utilizar tus lecciones avanzadas. He tenido suerte."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1706
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_10445a0d:

    # Ma "Lucky indeed, not to have found yourself in such need."
    Ma "Qué suerte, no haberte encontrado en tal necesidad."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1707
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_e54f4804:

    # Ma "I trust you are taking good care of my little toys?"
    Ma "Confío en que estás cuidando bien de mis pequeños juguetes."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1710
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_0629a1d2:

    # S "Yes Lady [Ma], I apply your teachings on how to keep my weapons in good order daily."
    S "Sí Señora [Ma], aplico a diario tus enseñanzas sobre cómo mantener mis armas en buen estado."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1711
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_823af04e:

    # Ma "Good."
    Ma "Bien."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1716
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_81420f2c:

    # S "My [persistent.dad] has actually started to take me along on his adventures.."
    S "Mi [persistent.dad] ha empezado a llevarme en sus aventuras.."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1719
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_2d16ce15:

    # Ma "Has he, really? I am sure you have made him proud."
    Ma "¿Lo ha hecho, de verdad? Estoy segura de que le habrás hecho sentirse orgulloso."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1722
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_a1b12093:

    # S "Well, it has been touch and go in a few moments, but I am still here."
    S "Bueno, ha sido un contacto con algunos personajes, pero aún estoy aquí."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1727
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_continue_f3605785:

    # S "I've even fought against mummies for the first time."
    S "Incluso he luchado contra las momias por primera vez."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1728
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_continue_b9fce71e:

    # Ma "That's impressive. Maybe we should meet, one of these days, for a refresher lesson..."
    Ma "Es impresionante. Quizá deberíamos quedar, un día de estos, para una lección de repaso..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1729
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_continue_fd18a9f7:

    # Ma "...so you can tell me more about these adventures..."
    Ma "... para que me cuentes más sobre esas aventuras..."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1732
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_continue_42163c09:

    # Sl "Pardon me, Mistress. The workers ask if they can go on their lunch break now."
    Sl "Perdóneme, Ama. Los trabajadores preguntan si pueden ir ya a su descanso para comer."

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1734
translate spanish d4b_mandisa_talk_continue_13ac5130:

    # Ma "You dog! Don't you see I'm talking to a valued customer?! Get lost!"
    Ma "¡Perro! ¿No ves que estoy hablando con una valiosa clienta? ¡Piérdete!"

# game/scripts/day4.rpy:1735
